Project Note #3 — Model Selection Complete

Observation

Benchmarked gemma3:4b vs qwen3:8b on multiple email types.
Summary quality was comparable.
Qwen consistently took 10–15x longer.

Results

Gemma: ~10–16 sec/email
Qwen: ~90–150 sec/email

Decision

Use gemma3:4b as the default summarization model for Email Agent v1.
Reserve qwen3:8b for future ARIA tasks requiring deeper reasoning.

Lesson

Benchmarking should stop once a clear winner emerges.
Development effort is better spent advancing project functionality than continuing tests with obvious outcomes.

Next Step

Return focus to Outlook authentication and email retrieval.


